                    <h3>How I Met Your Mother</h3>
                    <br>
                    <h4 id="himym_synopsis">Synopsis</h4>
                    <p>How I Met Your Mother is a TV sitcom set in New York City. The story revolves around 5 close friends living in <abbr title="New&nbsp;York">NY</abbr> and often hanging out together. The main plot is Future Ted telling his children the journey he has gone through resulting with him meeting their mother, which makes most of the show full of flashbacks. The show mostly contains of comedy and romance.</p>
                    <br>
                    <h4 id="himym_characters">Main characters</h4><br>
                    <table class="character-table">
                        <tr>
                            <td><img src="/img/himym/himym_tm.png" alt="Ted Mosby" width="240" height="240"></td>
                            <td><b>Ted Mosby</b><br><i>portrayed by Josh Radnor</i><br>A successful architect who likes to tell people facts he finds interesting and always corrects people's mistakes. Although he is friendly and kind, people can sometimes find him boring because of these characteristics of his. One of the oldest members of "the gang". His future self tells the whole story of the show.</td>
                        </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td><img src="/img/himym/himym_rs.png" alt="Robin Scherbatsky" width="240" height="240"></td>
                            <td><b>Robin Scherbatsky</b><br><i>portrayed by Cobie Smulders</i><br>A TV news anchor struggling through her way to become successful at her career. She joins the gang after she moves from Canada, her homeland, to New York in the pilot episode of the show. She's often joked about being Canadian. Doesn't like to let her emotions show.</td>
                          </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td><img src="/img/himym/himym_bs.png" alt="Barney Stinson" width="240" height="240"></td>
                            <td><b>Barney Stinson</b><br><i>portrayed by Neil Patrick Harris</i><br>Newest member of the gang after Scherbatsky. Likes to hang out in bars and is obsessed with suits so much that he wears suits almost all the time. Not much is known about his life apart from the gang including his occupation, however it is obvious that he earns great money.</td>
                          </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td><img src="/img/himym/himym_me.png" alt="Marshall Eriksen" width="240" height="240"></td>
                            <td><b>Marshall Eriksen</b><br><i>portrayed by Jason Segel</i><br>A lawyer who was born and raised in the northern part of the country. Tallest member of the gang as he is over 190 cms. Very emotional. He's so superstitious that he believes in myths like Big Foot, Loch Ness Monster (or as he calls her 'Nessie') and aliens. College friends with Mosby and Aldrin. Engaged with Aldrin.
                              </td>
                          </tr>
                          <tr>
                            <td><img src="/img/himym/himym_la.png" alt="Lily Aldrin" width="240" height="240"></td>
                            <td><b>Lily Aldrin</b><br><i>portrayed by Alyson Hannigan</i><br>Kindergarten teacher who is also one of the most emotionals in the squad. Interested in art. She wants to attend to an art school and become a successful artist exhibiting and selling her paintings one day. Engaged with Eriksen.</td>
                          </tr>
                    </table>
